Title: Sanguinarium
Plot: A link to the four witches Sabbaths is found after a doctor loses control and kills a patient on the operating table, and Mulder suspects a nurse may be practicing witchcraft.
GuestStars: O-Lan Jones, Richard Beymer, Arlene Mazerolle, Gregory Thirloway, John Juliani, Martin Evans, Paul Raskin, Andrew Airlie, Marie Stillin, Norman Armour, Nancy J. Lilley, Celine Lockhart, Nina Roman
